    "eyebrow": "Application",
    "num": "21",
    "deck": "<div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"eyebrow anim\"><span class=\"num\">21</span><span class=\"bar\"></span>Application</div><h2 class=\"head anim\">Simulating a Provisional Government Meeting</h2><ul><li>Role-play decision-making on governance challenges</li><li>Debate resource allocation and military strategy</li><li>Negotiate internal divisions and external threats</li></ul><p class=\"lede anim\">This activity applies knowledge of the provisional government’s challenges by engaging learners in a simulated meeting to experience political complexities firsthand. <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s5\">[5]</sup> <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s21\">[21]</sup></p><div class=\"lesson-detail anim\"><p><strong>Example:</strong> Participants represent different factions debating troop deployment and funding priorities.</p><p><strong>Practice:</strong> Assume a role and propose solutions to governance issues faced by the provisional government.</p><p><strong>Watch for:</strong> Focusing only on military concerns without considering political implications.</p></div><div id=\"quiz-slide21\" class=\"quizbox popquiz anim\" data-quiz=\"[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;mc&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:2,&quot;q&quot;:&quot;Which of the following groups had divided loyalties during the Texas Revolution?&quot;,&quot;options&quot;:[&quot;Anglo-American settlers&quot;,&quot;Tejanos&quot;,&quot;Enslaved African Americans&quot;,&quot;All of the above&quot;],&quot;answer&quot;:3,&quot;why&quot;:&quot;All these groups had complex and sometimes conflicting loyalties, reflecting the internal divisions during the revolution.&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;sa&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:3,&quot;q&quot;:&quot;Analyze how Santa Anna&#39;s centralist policies influenced the outbreak of the Texas Revolution.&quot;,&quot;rubric&quot;:&quot;Response should explain the shift from federalism to centralism under Santa Anna, how this alienated Texan settlers, and contributed to political tensions leading to revolution. Use examples from primary sources or historical evidence.&quot;,&quot;sample&quot;:&quot;Santa Anna&#39;s centralist policies replaced the 1824 Constitution&#39;s federalist system, reducing Texas&#39; autonomy. This angered settlers who valued local control, leading to resistance and eventually revolution.&quot;,&quot;accept&quot;:[&quot;Santa Anna&#39;s centralist policies reduced Texas autonomy and caused tensions&quot;,&quot;The shift from federalism to centralism upset Texan settlers&quot;,&quot;Centralist policies led to political conflict that sparked the revolution&quot;]}]\" data-pop=\"1\"></div></div>",
