    "eyebrow": "Transfer",
    "num": "22",
    "deck": "<div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"eyebrow anim\"><span class=\"num\">22</span><span class=\"bar\"></span>Transfer</div><h2 class=\"head anim\">Comparing Texas Revolution Governance to Other Revolutions</h2><ul><li>Identify similarities in provisional government challenges</li><li>Analyze differences in political and social contexts</li><li>Apply lessons from Texas to broader revolutionary studies</li></ul><p class=\"lede anim\">Comparing the Texas provisional government with those in other revolutions helps learners transfer understanding of governance challenges across historical contexts. <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s5\">[5]</sup> <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s21\">[21]</sup></p><div class=\"lesson-detail anim\"><p><strong>Example:</strong> Contrast Texas’s provisional government with the American Continental Congress during the Revolutionary War.</p><p><strong>Practice:</strong> Discuss how resource scarcity and internal divisions affected both governments.</p><p><strong>Watch for:</strong> Assuming all revolutionary governments face identical challenges without context.</p></div></div>",
