    "eyebrow": "Practice Checkpoint",
    "num": "29",
    "deck": "<div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"eyebrow anim\"><span class=\"num\">29</span><span class=\"bar\"></span>Practice Checkpoint</div><h2 class=\"head anim\">Review: Causes and Outcomes of the Texas Revolution</h2><ul><li>Recall key political causes leading to the revolution</li><li>Identify major battles and their significance</li><li>Explain the roles of different groups in the conflict</li><li>Summarize immediate and long-term outcomes</li></ul><p class=\"lede anim\">This checkpoint helps consolidate understanding of the revolution’s causes, key events, and consequences, ensuring readiness for deeper analysis and application. <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s2\">[2]</sup> <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s5\">[5]</sup> <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s21\">[21]</sup> <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s22\">[22]</sup></p><div class=\"lesson-detail anim\"><p><strong>Example:</strong> Recall how Santa Anna’s centralist policies contributed to tensions and how the Battle of San Jacinto secured independence.</p><p><strong>Practice:</strong> Write a brief summary connecting the causes, key battles, and outcomes of the Texas Revolution.</p><p><strong>Watch for:</strong> Focusing only on battles without understanding political and social contexts.</p></div><div id=\"quiz-slide29\" class=\"quizbox popquiz anim\" data-quiz=\"[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;mc&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:2,&quot;q&quot;:&quot;Which of the following groups had divided loyalties during the Texas Revolution?&quot;,&quot;options&quot;:[&quot;Anglo-American settlers&quot;,&quot;Tejanos&quot;,&quot;Enslaved African Americans&quot;,&quot;All of the above&quot;],&quot;answer&quot;:3,&quot;why&quot;:&quot;All these groups had complex and sometimes conflicting loyalties, reflecting the internal divisions during the revolution.&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;sa&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:3,&quot;q&quot;:&quot;Analyze how Santa Anna&#39;s centralist policies influenced the outbreak of the Texas Revolution.&quot;,&quot;rubric&quot;:&quot;Response should explain the shift from federalism to centralism under Santa Anna, how this alienated Texan settlers, and contributed to political tensions leading to revolution. Use examples from primary sources or historical evidence.&quot;,&quot;sample&quot;:&quot;Santa Anna&#39;s centralist policies replaced the 1824 Constitution&#39;s federalist system, reducing Texas&#39; autonomy. This angered settlers who valued local control, leading to resistance and eventually revolution.&quot;,&quot;accept&quot;:[&quot;Santa Anna&#39;s centralist policies reduced Texas autonomy and caused tensions&quot;,&quot;The shift from federalism to centralism upset Texan settlers&quot;,&quot;Centralist policies led to political conflict that sparked the revolution&quot;]}]\" data-pop=\"1\"></div></div>",
